Second, relying on central gatekeepers often leaves artists subject to the whims of those they are presenting their work to. It's a type of censorship where you can't make money of your creations if they don't fit what the major players desire. We as audiences forget that just a select group of well-known figures at the top chooses everything that gets to us. We all lose when large platforms prioritize business over diversity in their quest for maximum revenue. With Web3, everyone with an internet connection and a cryptocurrency wallet has the opportunity of pursuing a creative career because there are no gatekeepers dictating who and what receives a worldwide platform. Tokenized assets and the smart contracts they run on enable creators to monetize and control their inventions on their own terms, while decentralized platforms and metaverses provide them access to a global market.

Second, relying on central gatekeepers often leaves artists subject to the whims of those they are presenting their work to. It's a type of censorship where you can't make money of your creations if they don't fit what the major players desire. We as audiences forget that just a select group of well-known figures at the top chooses everything that gets to us. We all lose when large platforms prioritize business over diversity in their quest for maximum revenue. With Web3, everyone with an internet connection and a cryptocurrency wallet has the opportunity of pursuing a creative career because there are no gatekeepers dictating who and what receives a worldwide platform. Tokenized assets and the smart contracts they run on enable creators to monetize and control their inventions on their own terms, while decentralized platforms and metaverses provide them access to a global market.
